## downloading the data provided by the authors
## makke sure you have enough space and internet connection to store the data

#first check if you have google chrome on your system
if you don't then follow instructions on 
https://linuxize.com/post/how-to-install-google-chrome-web-browser-on-ubuntu-18-04/
to download the google chrome

launch google chrome and follow this link
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/curlwget/jmocjfidanebdlinpbcdkcmgdifblncg?hl=en
to add curlwget extension to your browser

next you get a sharable link from google drive and 
paste into a new tab and download

cancel the download before it reaches completion and click on the 
curlwget icon to view the wget and downloadable link syntax

copy and paste this into your terminal

